Description.Text:
Situated in the heart of London, Blades Hotel is a privately-run hotel offering a friendly welcome and personal attention. It is located in London's central area of Pimlico, close to Victoria, Westminster and Belgravia. Blades Hotel is conveniently situated in a quiet, residential area within walking distance of many famous landmarks such as Buckingham Palace, Westminster Abbey, The Tate Gallery, Harrods, the Houses of Parliament and many theaters and museums.


CANCELLATION POLICY;
We take a one night deposit from a credit card to secure all reservations, which is fully refundable subject to our 5 day cancellation policy (1 room). Bookings for 2 or more rooms will be subject to 7 full days cancellation policy. Cancellations are required in writing;  letter, fax or email please.  Cancellation policy varies over the Christmas/New Year Period.  (We regret that we do not accept American Express or Diners Club credit cards).
